# Video assets — drop files here
#
# Expected files (see index.html hero section):
#   hero-loop.mp4   — Hero background video loop (H.264)
#   hero-loop.webm  — Hero background video loop (WebM, optional fallback)
#
# Recommended specs:
#   Resolution: 1920×1080 or 2560×1440
#   Duration: 10–30 seconds, seamless loop
#   No audio track (muted autoplay)
#   File size: under 5 MB for fast load